<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] [passage omitted] France has ruled out any 
further military intervention in Rwanda such as its intervention 
between October 1990 to December 1993. [passage omitted]. 
  The French cooperation minister has moreover said that more 
than 50 Rwandan ministers and high-ranking civil servants and 
their families have been taking refuge in the French Embassy in 
