<H3> <TI>   Police Clarify Residence Permit Policy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Police Clarify Residence Permit Policy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0604141394 The Hague ANP Nieuwsberichten Database in Dutch 
1911 GMT 5 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0604141394 </F>
<F P=104>  The Hague ANP Nieuwsberichten Database </F>
<F P=105>  Dutch </F>


