<H3> <TI>   Tories Intensify Their Spring Election Offensive </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tories Intensify Their Spring Election Offensive </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1204091094 London THE GUARDIAN in English 12 Apr 94 p 
1--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM1204091094 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE GUARDIAN </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


