<DATE1>  11 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kanther Not Planning To Ban Republikaner </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kanther Not Planning To Ban Republikaner </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1104185894 Mainz ZDF Television Network in German 1700 GMT 
11 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1104185894 </F>
<F P=104>  Mainz ZDF Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] For the time being, FRG Interior Minister Kanther 
does not plan to ban the right-wing extremist Republikaner. He 
does not think that an application for a ban to the Federal 
Constitutional Court would have a chance. The material that the 
constitutional protection officers have collected on the party 
so far is not sufficient for a ban, Kanther said. Instead, he 
recommended struggling against the Repulikaner with political 
means and ostracizing them in society. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

