<H3> <TI>   Lamassoure on Extension of Strikes </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Lamassoure on Extension of Strikes </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1204104194 Paris Radio France International in French 0900 
