  [Text] In Madrid, Russian Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev, 
who is accompanying Russian President Boris Yeltsin on his visit 
to Spain, has just referred to the situation in Bosnia. Over to 
the radio car at the Viana Palace. Angel Garcia, good afternoon. 
  [Garcia] Good afternoon. Russian Foreign Minister Kozyrev 
