translation] Making such a decision without counting on Russia 
means taking a very big risk. [end recording] 
  [Garcia] According to Kozyrev, the NATO air strikes against 
Serbian positions could backfire because they might make the 
conflict worse. That is why he also described the decision as 
hasty. That is all for the time being. 

