  [Text] Sweden's Defense Minister Anders Bjorck says the 
Bosnian Serbs must know NATO will take even tougher action 
against them if the Serbs directly attack the UN peacekeeping 
troops. Sweden supports the NATO raids even if Sweden is not a 
member of the defense alliance. Swedish troops are part of the 
Nordic UN battalion now serving in Bosnia. 

